@div barsud A

1. ur-saŋ a₂-ŋal₂ {d}a-nun-na-ke₄-ne e₂-kur-ta [e₃-a]
#lem: ursaŋ[warrior]; aŋal[strong]; Anunak[1]DN; Ekur[1]TN; e[leave]
#etcsl: line-id=A.1

#note: Cited in OB catalogue from Urim (U3), 0.2.05, Seg. A, line 3

2. {d}nin-urta en {d}nu-nam-nir-re u₁₈-lu gal-gin₇# [...] X
#lem: Ninurtak[1]DN; en[lord]; Nunamnir[1]DN; ulu[south wind]; gal[big]; X; X
#etcsl: line-id=A.2

3. mu-un-tu-ud-de₃-en u₃-ma-ni gub-bu-de₃ gu₃ ma#-[ra]-de₂#
#lem: utud[give birth (to)]; uma[triumph]; gub[stand]; gu[voice]; de[pour]
#etcsl: line-id=A.3

@div trailer 

4. bar-sud-am₃
#lem: barsud[musical notation]
#etcsl: line-id=A.4

@end trailer

@end barsud

@div cagbatuku B

5. {d}nin-tur₅-re šu niŋ₂ dim₂-ma-ni za-ra mu-ri-in-bad
#lem: Nintur[1]DN; šu[hand]; niŋ[thing]; dim[create]; zaʾe[you]; bad[open]
#etcsl: line-id=B.5

6. ubur dug₃-ga-na ka ma-ra-ni-in-ba ga nam-šul-la mi-ri-in-gu₇
#lem: ubur[breast]; dug[good]; kag[mouth]; ba[allot]; ga[milk]; namšul[manhood]; gu[eat]
#etcsl: line-id=B.6

7. am u₆ di-gin₇ alan-zu mu-un-er₉ a₂-ur₂-zu mu-un-gur₄
#lem: am[wild bull]; u[admiration]; di[speak]; alan[image]; ir[mighty]; aʾur[limbs]; gur[thick]
#etcsl: line-id=B.7

8. igi ni₂ bur₂-e en me-lem₄ nam-ur-saŋ da-da-ra-še₃ mi-ri-in-dug₄
#lem: igi[eye]; ni[self]; bur[spread out]; en[lord]; melim[frightening splendor]; namursaŋ[heroism]; dadara[tied up]; dug[speak]
#etcsl: line-id=B.8

9. kišib-la₂ zid-da-zu im-ma-an-dab₅ ama-zu {d}nin-tur₅-re
#lem: kišibla[wrist]; zid[right]; dab[seize]; ama[mother]; Nintur[1]DN
#etcsl: line-id=B.9

